ques.p: To ask the Secretary of State for Transport pursuant to the Answer of 8 May 2008, Official Report, columns 1062-6W, on departmental public participation, how much each (a) survey and (b) piece of qualitative research cost; and how many participants there were in each.

reply.p: The additional information requested about services by polling companies to the Department in 2007-08 is included in the tables.

As before these included ongoing surveys (table A), ad-hoc surveys (table B) and qualitative research (table C). Additional information has become available since the response to PQ 2579 and the tables have been amended to reflect this.
